Microsoft Dynamics CRM Functional Consultant Montash City of London (EC1), City of London £450 - £550 per day Montash Contract Posted 7 days ago
Activate one-click apply. What is one-click apply? Microsoft Dynamics 365 Functional Consultant required with strong CRM knowledge. Joining this exciting project on an initial 9 month contract (likely to be extended).
If you have a passion for CRM and enjoy designing and implementing leading-edge technical solutions to deliver on complex business requirements, we want to hear from you!
Day to Day:
The role includes working with customers' technical, business and management teams to understand their strategy and identify their 'must have' requirements, in order to extend and re-design existing parts of their platform You will be involved at all stages of engagement - from pre-sales through to requirements capture, business analysis and technical solution design You will be hands-on in developing and leading the implementation of Dynamics CRM solutions for our customers in the public and private sectors.
Skills Range:
3+ years Microsoft Dynamics CRM project experience Ability to analyse requirements, design and configure features in Dynamics 365/CRM. Good understanding of implementing Dynamics CRM extensions such as plugins, custom workflows and JavaScript Strong working knowledge of associated technologies including Microsoft Dynamics CRM Outlook Client, Office 365, Authentication and Active Directory A good facilitator and strong personality, able to manage multiple stakeholders.
Personal Specification:
Customer orientated, strategic thinker, commercially focussed Excellent communication skills; written, verbal and facilitation Good interpersonal skills, able to build long-term relationships with new and existing clients and partners Highly organised including ability to organise own and others to achieve deadlines Great attention to detail with accuracy and love of perfection
